  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join the community</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>THE LAST HUMAN IS A BIKER (TLH) combines shooter and runner mechanics to deliver a fast-paced gameplay, spiced up with roguelite elements.</strong><br><br>\"<i>2666, an alien invasion destroyed the USA. John is the only survivor, the last human. Embark in a vengeful adventure on the United States devastated roads, and destroy alien scums with big guns and tasty punchlines.</i>\"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Drive - Kill - Die - Repeat</h2><br>Survive as long as possible.<br>Collect resources to upgrade your stash.<br>Start again with your new toys.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/76900790bc1989ceaab2913b8cf59431.poster.avif?t=1684742504\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/76900790bc1989ceaab2913b8cf59431.webm?t=1684742504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/76900790bc1989ceaab2913b8cf59431.mp4?t=1684742504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gear up and kick ass</h2><br>Choose your starting weapon and bike. <br>Smash some aliens to level up.<br>Upgrade your gear to the top.<br>Make yourself the real boss.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/d3c4a0a3f977a6845147a7c2c1906450.poster.avif?t=1684742504\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/d3c4a0a3f977a6845147a7c2c1906450.webm?t=1684742504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/d3c4a0a3f977a6845147a7c2c1906450.mp4?t=1684742504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The right tool for the right man</h2><br>Combine your modules with no limit.<br>Find the funniest combination possible.<br>These various combinations will make each game unique.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/a1ccb38c2911d220ac3687ac0c275279.poster.avif?t=1684742504\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/a1ccb38c2911d220ac3687ac0c275279.webm?t=1684742504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/a1ccb38c2911d220ac3687ac0c275279.mp4?t=1684742504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Show your friends who's the best</h2><br>Score the most points in each mode.<br>Take position in the online leaderboard.<br>Support them or make fun of them.<br>That's up to you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/cfb624e253d69c3a8cd148e4bf08f320.poster.avif?t=1684742504\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/cfb624e253d69c3a8cd148e4bf08f320.webm?t=1684742504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/cfb624e253d69c3a8cd148e4bf08f320.mp4?t=1684742504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shut up and take my punchlines</h2><br>“<i>Since it's the '90s, you don't just smack a guy in the face. You say something cool first.</i>” - Joe Hallenbeck (Bruce Willis) in The Last Boy Scout.<br><br>This game is a tribute to 90s movies and series masterpiece, from THE RENEGADE to AKIRA, including MAD MAX and STARSHIP TROOPERS. Every breath you take, prepare for a shower of cultural references to awaken Nostalgia.",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>THE LAST HUMAN IS A BIKER (TLH) combines shooter and runner mechanics to deliver a fast-paced gameplay, spiced up with roguelite elements.</strong><br><br>\"<i>2666, an alien invasion destroyed the USA. John is the only survivor, the last human. Embark in a vengeful adventure on the United States devastated roads, and destroy alien scums with big guns and tasty punchlines.</i>\"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Drive - Kill - Die - Repeat</h2><br>Survive as long as possible.<br>Collect resources to upgrade your stash.<br>Start again with your new toys.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/76900790bc1989ceaab2913b8cf59431.poster.avif?t=1684742504\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/76900790bc1989ceaab2913b8cf59431.webm?t=1684742504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/76900790bc1989ceaab2913b8cf59431.mp4?t=1684742504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gear up and kick ass</h2><br>Choose your starting weapon and bike. <br>Smash some aliens to level up.<br>Upgrade your gear to the top.<br>Make yourself the real boss.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/d3c4a0a3f977a6845147a7c2c1906450.poster.avif?t=1684742504\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/d3c4a0a3f977a6845147a7c2c1906450.webm?t=1684742504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1999470/extras/d3c4a0a3f977a6845147a7c2c1906450.mp4?t=1684742504\" type=\"video/mp4\